{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it was pitch dark.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we lost two of the boys, never heard of them again, never knew what actually happened to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were 14.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we got across, away from the German border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then there was some more shooting, and, you know, anyway, we managed to get across that border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We managed to get across to the other side, and we were met there by a different guide who then, over a period of days, took us to a place called Maribor.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I don't want to stay on this whole escapade day by day because--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took us to a place called Maribor, which was the closest city to-- that we came to.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in Croatia at this time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, at this stage, two cars were supposed to meet us, and this was part of the organization from Zagreb, which was probably another 100 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or maybe not even that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly the distances.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew our destination was Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is where the Recha Freier was sitting, waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I say sitting, she was-- that was where her organization was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so when we arrived in Maribor, at the appointed time, only one car turned up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, you can't put 10 children into one car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Five had to stay behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The promise was that the car would come back the next day and pick us up, or another car.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it never came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It turned out-- and the driver told us, if you can find, there's a Jewish family, they are called Deutsch.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Deitz?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Deutsch?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a timber merchant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He will hide you for a day or the night, and that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
